name: Retrieve Channel Usage for valid CIF Key having logged into Application

testSteps.description: Given I logged into the API earlier
And I have confirmed a Customer with a cif Key "0100000930000139000"

When I fetch the Channel Utilisation Details for CIF Key <cifKey>:
| cifKey |
| 0100000930000139000 |

Then the following Channel Utilisation data should be returned
| internetBankingUsed | mobileBankingUsed | tabletBankingUsed | phoneBankingUsed | branchBankingUsed | kioskBankingUsed | iDDCreditUsed | atmUsed | pointOfSaleUsed | anPostUsed | smallBusinessIntenetBankingUsed | internetBusinessBankingUsed | lastUsedInternetBankinge | lastUsedMobileBanking | lastUsedTabletBanking | lastUsedPhoneBanking | lastUsedBranchBanking | lastUsedKioskBanking | lastUsedIDDCredit | lastUsedATM | lastUsedPOS | lastUsedAnPost | lastUsed24hrSIBIB | ibbLastLogon | registrationNumber |
| false | false | false | false | false | false | false | false | false | false | false | false | null | null | null | null | null | null | null | null | null | null | null | null |  |
